trans-unit.source: A lookup table specifies how existing color channel values should be replaced by new values.

seg-source.mrk: A lookup table specifies how existing color channel values should be replaced by new values.

target.mrk: A lookup table specifies how existing color channel values should be replaced by new values.

trans-unit.source: A color channel value of j is replaced by the jth entry in the lookup table for that channel.

seg-source.mrk: A color channel value of j is replaced by the jth entry in the lookup table for that channel.

target.mrk: A color channel value of j is replaced by the jth entry in the lookup table for that channel.

trans-unit.source: For example, an existing blue channel value of 25 would be replaced by the value of $aColorLUT[25][3].
